title: What is Demand Avoidance? A Guide for Teenagers
description:
In this course for teenagers, Naomi discusses the times when everything feels like pressure and your nervous system and how it works. She describes the pressure trap - how we can sometimes get into a trap when we feel under pressure - and how we can do things to help by building the world that works for you and by befriending your nervous system.
With short videos featuring Chloe from Me Just Me.
